{"id": "1459582253603750173", "channel_id": "1459555990478524569", "type": 19, "author_id": "139343733714845697", "author_name": "satachan", "author_bot": false, "content": "My goal is only to just leave a ping for the devs to know that wanda enjoyers still exist. \n\nWe all know how much they have been trying to move away from ultra counter and with ultra always getting memed on despite being in a solid spot right now, they're trying to build a new image for the ultra realm awakers. \n\nI wouldn't like to see an awaker get forgotten in a game about rememberance.", "timestamp": "2026-01-10T16:18:46.986000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["706262934485073951"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🦐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1459567310007308515", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1459555990478524569", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Possibilty of rebalancing Wanda?", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801", "1361169005435420785"]}
